title: Kid Made Modern Christmas Card Making Kit
description:
It's easy to make your own festive cards with the Christmas Card Making Kit! Includes blank cards and envelopes with gem and felt stickers, chunky mini markers, googly eyes & more. Your friends and family will love receiving these holiday creations made especially for them. Perfect activity for playtime with friends. Recommended for ages 6 and up. Includes:

  • 6 – 4x6” blank folded cards
  • 7 kraft envelopes
  • 5 chunky mini markers
  • 36 assorted felt stickers
  • 6 sticker-backed googly eyes
  • 6 – 4x4” cardstock sheets
  • 31 assorted sticker gems
  • 40 glue dots
  • 34 assorted paillettes
  • 2 – 6x9” sticker sheets
  • 1 santa letter template
